<sect1 id="dir_554e74df1a63d9585349b46f0a64af7c_1autotoc_md157">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::input</title><para>Input handling systems for game entities.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_554e74df1a63d9585349b46f0a64af7c_1autotoc_md158">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides input-related functionality for the game layer, including systems that translate device input (gamepads, keyboards) into game commands.</para>
</sect1>
